Package com.saxonica.jaxp Description

This package contains those Saxon-SA classes that are dependent on JAXP 1-3 (which is part of J2SE 5.0, but is not part of JDK 1-4).

The classes in this package are delivered as a separate JAR file, saxon8sa-jaxp.jar. This JAR file needs to be on the classpath if JAXP 1-3 interfaces are used by the application, and it does not need to be on the classpath otherwise. The effect of this separation is that the other parts of Saxon-SA, which are delivered in the JAR file saxon8sa.jar, run on JDK 1.4 as issued.
